title: Examkrackers MCAT Review 2015
description:
Included in this torrent are scans of each review book in the 9th Edition Examkrackers MCAT Complete Study Package for the 2015 MCAT. There should be 6 PDF files:

- EK Biology 1 - Molecules.pdf
- EK Biology 2 - Systems.pdf
- EK Chemistry.pdf
- EK Physics.pdf
- EK Psychology & Sociology.pdf
- EK Verbal Reasoning.pdf

I OCRed all the scans and added bookmarks to them to make it easier to jump between sections as needed. I was a little pressed for time when scanning, so all the pages aren't perfect, but all the information is there and legible.

Good luck studying and remember to seed!
